item.title: By: stephen
item.dc:creator: stephen
item.description: this particular cafe racer is quite unique, the seat section needs a new design, but other than that, the whole bike is amazing. GREAT design, but that street racing bump behind the seat is killing the bikes natural vibe. the extended back end is awesome for the style too! consider a new seat. maybe an old-school cafe seat? GOOD JOB !!
